title: How should we use the Ethereum from the first round of secondary sales?
body:
We promised holders that delisting will entitle them to ethereum distribution from the very first round of secondary sales. Many have suggested we use them towards marketing. We will be doing NFT airdrops to holders soon.

This proposal requests a vote on: Should we use them for marketing instead?
author: 0x355a65a72Cceb66029cACC7C027202bf5b4Fe278
